PC Number Date Chapter Bill Dept
 2023-00402023-01-31DND
ActNational Defence Act
SubjectOrder authorizing the delivery of non-surplus materials to Ukraine
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of National Defence to deliver to the Department of Public Works and Government Services, for disposal to Ukraine, additional materiel of a value that does not exceed $125 million, that has not been declared surplus, and is not immediately required for use by the Canadian Armed Forces or for any other purposes under the Act.
